name: MOSAYCS - #0 - Rising Sun
description: Mosaic is an ancient art that is present in several civilizations around the world and is one of the oldest forms of artistic expression of humanity. Many civilizations have recorded their history using this technique. In addition, artists such as Jorge Selarón, Burle Marx, Invader, Tomie Ohtake, Cláudia Sperb, Ligia Klarc, Antoni Gaudi, Rodrigo de Haro and many other artists and artisans who used this form of expression served as inspiration for this project to be born. Created by Yule Aurêh (@yuleaureh), this is the beginning of the MOSAYCS project - exclusive gallery at Hic et Nunc 2000.
